            "text": "<p>Enhance your Arccos experience by combining the Arccos Air AI wearable with the Smart Laser Rangefinder. The Smart Laser works seamlessly with an Arccos Game Tracking subscription to automatically set the pin location in the app simply by shooting the flag, so you can get more accurate personalized data to improve all aspects of your game.</p>",
